AUDIO: 'need to do that again later with a proper example so you guys can see what that looks like. But for character swapping alone, even the camera angles follow up pretty well with scale 2. Compared to scale one, the preview'

[11:34] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'version, the image quality is noticeably better. Character fidelity, physics, all improved. For example, this guy wearing the gray jacket. You can see the jacket movement is being affected by the physics of the'

[11:47] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'motion. And that reference doesn\'t come from the original source video. The source video has two topless boxers, so there\'s no control net or depth map referencing the jacket movement. This is all based purely on transferring the'

[12:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
