[12:27] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'is totally different in the first frames, I found that scale 2 can use the object tracking to handle it. You can even see the cartoon character showing up a P sign, which is a completely different pose from the reference video'

[12:40] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'character, and it still works for the video animation. In these examples, I turned off replacement mode, so it\'s also using the cartoon character\'s background in the video output.'

[12:52] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
